long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cubby is a collaborative research tool for people who power-share links. Unlike sharing in Notion or Slack, Cubby has native annotation tools on top of all content posted. Cubby also helps you keep all your content organized in one place with your team.
